Mary! Clarence!

2063
02:00:36,320 --> 02:00:37,840
Get out of here!

2064
02:00:37,880 --> 02:00:41,960
- Clarence!
- Where are you?

2065
02:00:42,040 --> 02:00:43,360
Oh, it's you!

2066
02:00:46,680 --> 02:00:47,920
Stand back!

2067
02:01:02,040 --> 02:01:03,240
Clarence!

2068
02:01:08,280 --> 02:01:10,880
Clarence! Clarence!

2069
02:01:12,120 --> 02:01:13,440
Help me, Clarence.

2070
02:01:14,920 --> 02:01:16,040
Get me back.

2071
02:01:17,200 --> 02:01:19,400
Get me back. I don't
care what happens to me.

2072
02:01:20,440 --> 02:01:22,440
Get me back to my wife and kids.

2073
02:01:23,000 --> 02:01:24,440
Help me, Clarence, please.

2074
02:01:25,600 --> 02:01:28,960
Please! I want to live again.

2075
02:01:29,000 --> 02:01:30,520
I want to live again.

2076
02:01:32,000 --> 02:01:33,560
I want to live again.

2077
02:01:33,640 --> 02:01:36,240
Please, God, let me live again.

