02:01:45,000 --> 02:01:46,040
Hey, George.

2079
02:01:47,840 --> 02:01:49,000
George!

2080
02:01:50,040 --> 02:01:52,080
You all right. Hey, what's the matter?

2081
02:01:52,120 --> 02:01:54,560
Now get out of here, Bert or
I'll hit you again! Get out!

2082
02:01:54,600 --> 02:01:56,480
What the Sam Hill you,
you yelling for, George!

2083
02:01:56,560 --> 02:02:01,040
You... George?

2084
02:02:01,120 --> 02:02:02,480
Bert, do you know me?

2085
02:02:02,520 --> 02:02:04,520
