2089
02:02:12,240 --> 02:02:13,360
What did you...

2090
02:02:17,640 --> 02:02:21,040
My mouth's bleeding,
Bert! My mouth's bleed...

2091
02:02:21,080 --> 02:02:24,160
Zuzu's petals,
Zuzu's... There they are!

2092
02:02:24,240 --> 02:02:27,080
Bert! What do you know about that?

2093
02:02:27,160 --> 02:02:29,520
Merry Christmas!

2094
02:02:29,560 --> 02:02:31,400
Well, Merry Christmas!

2095
02:02:31,440 --> 02:02:32,480
Mary!

2096
02:02:33,400 --> 02:02:34,680
Mary!

2097
02:02:35,960 --> 02:02:38,280
Yaa!

2098
02:02:41,880 --> 02:02:43,200
Yaa!

2099
02:02:43,240 --> 02:02:45,640
Hello, Bedford Falls!

2100
02:02:48,200 --> 02:02:51,400
- Merry Christmas!
- Merry Christmas!

2101
02:02:51,440 --> 02:02:53,400
Merry Christmas, George!

2102
02:02:53,440 --> 02:02:56,640
Merry Christmas, movie house!

